Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.99,0:02:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you can't go through with this belt...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.67,0:02:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? {\alpha&HFF&}Still doesn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.67,0:02:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Still doesn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... {\alpha&HFF&}we really don't have a choice but to accustom you to the security measures around here, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.72,0:02:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... we really don't have a choice but to accustom you to the security measures around here, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.69,0:02:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about... this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.55,0:02:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.81,0:02:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happened to your forehead?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.35,0:02:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I had a fight with my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.10,0:02:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My kid is still young, so it looks like I'm going to have to commute here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.86,0:02:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, {\alpha&HFF&}it would be better for you to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.04,0:02:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it would be better for you to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste! {\alpha&HFF&}The rooms here are incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste! The rooms here are incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.87,0:02:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just move in yourself, with the family and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat me like I'm a single, easy-going guy such as yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Ryuuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.42,0:02:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A date.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone on a date, along with Light-kun, in Misa-Misa's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.39,0:03:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surveillance cameras, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.02,0:03:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, {\alpha&HFF&}I guess it's unavoidable considering Amane is somehow connected to the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.83,0:03:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it's unavoidable considering Amane is somehow connected to the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Matsuda, stop calling her "Misa-Misa"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.82,0:03:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.87,0:03:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You know, for me, this just isn't feeling like a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, aren't you going to eat that cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet things make you fat, so I avoid them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you use your brain, you won't get fat, even if you eat sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! You're making fun of Misa again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. How about I give you the cake if you leave me and Light alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.87,0:03:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I leave you alone, I'd still be watching you on the surveillance cameras; it'll still be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pervert! Will you just quit with all this tasteless stuff, already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever you say, I'm still taking your cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.69,0:03:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. We'll just close the curtains and turn off the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cameras detect infrared as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.59,0:03:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, {\alpha&HFF&}despite moving into these headquarters filled with equipment, Ryuuzaki, you seem to lack the motivation to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.02,0:03:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, despite moving into these headquarters filled with equipment, {\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuzaki, you seem to lack the motivation to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:04:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, despite moving into these headquarters filled with equipment, Ryuuzaki, {\alpha&HFF&}you seem to lack the motivation to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, despite moving into these headquarters filled with equipment, Ryuuzaki, you seem to lack the motivation to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Motivation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.42,0:04:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I'm pretty depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Depressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I've always thought that Light-kun was Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}the idea that this theory may be wrong has come as quite a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I've always thought that Light-kun was Kira, the idea that this theory may be wrong has come as quite a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I have my suspicions...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hence the reason for these.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then again, Kira can manipulate people's actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.35,0:04:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, Kira was manipulating you in such a way that I would suspect you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.45,0:04:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both Light-kun and Misa-san were being manipulated by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think about it this way, it does seem to make sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.04,0:04:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By that reasoning, {\alpha&HFF&}even though Misa and I were being manipulated, we were still Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.49,0:04:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By that reasoning, even though Misa and I were being manipulated, we were still Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, {\alpha&HFF&}there's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.82,0:04:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, there's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're both Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to my theory, Light-kun was Kira when I imprisoned him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And from that moment, criminals stopped dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, the theory that Light-kun was Kira still worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, two weeks later, {\alpha&HFF&}criminals started dying again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, two weeks later, criminals started dying again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So from here, we move to the next assumption...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira's powers can be passed from person to person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an interesting theory, but if that's the case, then catching Kira will be no small feat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.30,0:05:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's why I'm stumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we catch those being manipulated, {\alpha&HFF&}their power will just pass to someone else, and no memory of it will remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we catch those being manipulated, their power will just pass to someone else, and no memory of it will remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many people we manage to catch, it'll be pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.46,0:05:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But none of this has been confirmed yet. {\alpha&HFF&}Try and rouse some motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.37,0:05:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But none of this has been confirmed yet. Try and rouse some motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Motivation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.67,0:05:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, it's probably better if we don't try too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:06:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we chase them too desperately, we'll just be placing our own lives at risk... {\alpha&HFF&}don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we chase them too desperately, we'll just be placing our own lives at risk... don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fuck with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.84,0:06:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no motivation because your little theory about me being Kira was wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I phrased that badly. {\alpha&HFF&}I meant that making the first move might work against us, so--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I phrased that badly. I meant that making the first move might work against us, so--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.93,0:06:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are we supposed to catch them if we don't even chase them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many innocent people do you think have already been entangled in this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, weren't you the one who imprisoned both Misa and myself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know... {\alpha&HFF&}but no matter what reasons you had, my motto is... an eye for an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know... but {\alpha&HFF&}no matter what reasons you had, my motto is... an eye for an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.63,0:06:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know... but no matter what reasons you had, my motto is... {\alpha&HFF&}an eye for an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know... but no matter what reasons you had, my motto is... an eye for an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that my theory was wrong, {\alpha&HFF&}merely that "Yagami Light is Kira" and "Amane Misa is the second Kira" wasn't enough to solve the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that my theory was wrong, merely that "Yagami Light is Kira" and "Amane Misa is the second Kira" wasn't enough to solve the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.41,0:07:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it so wrong for a human to feel this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say it was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.85,0:07:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way you're talking, {\alpha&HFF&}it sounds like you won't be satisfied unless I really am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way you're talking, it sounds like you won't be satisfied unless I really am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not satisfied unless Light-kun really is Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.26,0:07:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've only just realized... {\alpha&HFF&}I wanted you to be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've only just realized... I wanted you to be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember, an eye for an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.42,0:07:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fairly strong you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.99,0:08:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}We should contact them and get them to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We should contact them and get them to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki! Get this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa-Misa was voted top of the Eighteen readers' popularity poll!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.71,0:08:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This means that she'll be the star in Director Nishinaka's next movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just Matsuda being his usual dumb-ass self.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Matsuda-san is a bit of an airhead by nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear you both...
