Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.30,0:08:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, I know you've got no motivation for anything, but can you take a look at this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.57,0:08:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this carefully. {\alpha&HFF&}It seems like this might be hinting at something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this carefully. It seems like this might be hinting at something.
