Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All three of them died from heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:09:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, Yotsuba's share prices have risen, while those of other enterprises have fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simply put, {\alpha&HFF&}all these deaths have benefited Yotsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simply put, all these deaths have benefited Yotsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you search a little deeper, there have been thirteen incidents like this over the last three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.01,0:09:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only conclusion I can draw from this, is that Kira is backing Yotsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.33,0:09:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, {\alpha&HFF&}but if this is true, killing criminals isn't Kira's primary objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but if this is true, {\alpha&HFF&}killing criminals isn't Kira's primary objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but if this is true, killing criminals isn't Kira's primary objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.88,0:09:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, {\alpha&HFF&}it's possible that they're using the act of killing criminals as a camouflage for killing people for their own profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.07,0:09:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's possible that they're using the act of killing criminals as a camouflage for killing people for their own profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how's that? {\alpha&HFF&}Feeling slightly more motivated now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how's that? Feeling slightly more motivated now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impressive that everything is going this smoothly; nobody suspects anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both Yotsuba's share price and profits have gradually been rising without gaining attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is going exactly according to our calculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's just one thing that's been on my mind... {\alpha&HFF&}the three we killed last week... why did they all die of heart attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's just one thing that's been on my mind... the three we killed last week... {\alpha&HFF&}why did they all die of heart attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's just one thing that's been on my mind... the three we killed last week... why did they all die of heart attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For one of them, I thought we decided on an accidental death?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably because we specified the place of death as along the Wangansen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:17.01,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Wangansen is a coastal highway in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, at the time of his death, he wasn't at home, but was secretly with a woman in Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, {\alpha&HFF&}if there's an impossible element in the cause of death we provide...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.94,0:10:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if there's an impossible element in the cause of death we provide...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira will merely kill them with a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.03,0:10:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I said last week that if we just request for a death either via an accident or illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he'll eliminate them in the fastest and most natural way possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, {\alpha&HFF&}the police should already have their hands full investigating the deaths of criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the police should already have their hands full investigating the deaths of criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there was someone who was able to trace these civilian deaths back to us, {\alpha&HFF&}they would have to be some sort of god.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.95,0:10:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there was someone who was able to trace these civilian deaths back to us, they would have to be some sort of god.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, it's all been taken care of already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:10:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief! {\alpha&HFF&}Ah, Mogi-san! Thanks for all your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.66,0:10:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief! Ah, {\alpha&HFF&}Mogi-san! Thanks for all your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:10:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief! Ah, Mogi-san! {\alpha&HFF&}Thanks for all your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief! Ah, Mogi-san! Thanks for all your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing! {\alpha&HFF&}Thanks to Light-kun's work, there's a real possibility that Kira is connected to the Yotsuba Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing! Thanks to Light-kun's work, there's a real possibility that Kira is connected to the Yotsuba Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yotsuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably it, Matsuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.13,0:11:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, {\alpha&HFF&}I heard from the Deputy Chief that Kira has been sending bribes to politicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.06,0:11:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, I heard from the Deputy Chief that Kira has been sending bribes to politicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what Kira is promising... {\alpha&HFF&}in return for the police simply ceasing their pursuit of Kira, they would leave the politicians untouched.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what Kira is promising... in return for the police simply ceasing their pursuit of Kira, they would leave the politicians untouched.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.61,0:11:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police have sold out to Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mogi has already made his decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa, {\alpha&HFF&}Matsuda, if you still want to pursue Kira, you'll need to follow Mogi and myself, and hand in your resignations to the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa, Matsuda, {\alpha&HFF&}if you still want to pursue Kira, you'll need to follow Mogi and myself, and hand in your resignations to the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.23,0:11:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa, Matsuda, if you still want to pursue Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}you'll need to follow Mogi and myself, and hand in your resignations to the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.13,0:11:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa, Matsuda, if you still want to pursue Kira, you'll need to follow Mogi and myself, and hand in your resignations to the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless we decide to resign from the police, {\alpha&HFF&}we'll no longer be allowed to investigate Kira seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.26,0:11:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless we decide to resign from the police, we'll no longer be allowed to investigate Kira seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.39,0:11:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:11:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very simple. {\alpha&HFF&}They said that if I continue to investigate with L, I'll be fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.47,0:12:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very simple. They said that if I continue to investigate with L, {\alpha&HFF&}I'll be fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.25,0:12:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very simple. They said that if I continue to investigate with L, I'll be fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-{\alpha&HFF&}So, Chief, what did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.42,0:12:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So, Chief, what did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.86,0:12:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a few hours, I'll no longer be the Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.17,0:12:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you have your own lives, {\alpha&HFF&}so think carefully before you decide what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you have your own lives, so think carefully before you decide what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, {\alpha&HFF&}especially those with wives and children...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, especially those with wives and children...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that all of you should return to the police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I originally began alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful that you've all managed to stick with it for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll be able to do this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I promise to visit you all with Kira's head as a present to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, {\alpha&HFF&}as long as I'm here, you won't be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, as long as I'm here, you won't be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made this promise as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct. {\alpha&HFF&}Until Kira is caught, I'll need Yagami-kun to stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct. Until Kira is caught, I'll need Yagami-kun to stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.61,0:12:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the rest of you should return to the police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you once say that you needed the cooperation of the police with this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was because then, the police, as an organization, was prepared to disobey Kira and maintain its stance on this investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But help from a few civilians who have quit the police can't really be said to be with "the cooperation of the police".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police have decided not to catch Kira. {\alpha&HFF&}You've done enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.06,0:13:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police have decided not to catch Kira. You've done enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's true that if we leave the police, we may not be of much help to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but what about our feelings?! {\alpha&HFF&}We've put our lives on the line for this case!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but what about our feelings?! We've put our lives on the line for this case!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should have the right to decide by ourselves: do we want to continue investigating, or return to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so... {\alpha&HFF&}in that case, please make your own decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so... in that case, please make your own decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.39,0:13:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-{\alpha&HFF&}But Chief, by quitting the police we'll be without a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.98,0:13:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But Chief, {\alpha&HFF&}by quitting the police we'll be without a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But Chief, by quitting the police we'll be without a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we manage to catch Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}what are we supposed to do after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we manage to catch Kira, what are we supposed to do after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that? {\alpha&HFF&}I hadn't really thought of that, but I'm guessing that once we've caught Kira, we'd have to... find new jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:13:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that? I hadn't really thought of that, {\alpha&HFF&}but I'm guessing that once we've caught Kira, we'd have to... find new jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.26,0:14:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that? I hadn't really thought of that, but I'm guessing that once we've caught Kira, we'd have to... {\alpha&HFF&}find new jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that? I hadn't really thought of that, but I'm guessing that once we've caught Kira, we'd have to... find new jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided! {\alpha&HFF&}I'm going to quit the police and continue chasing Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.04,0:14:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided! I'm going to quit the police and continue chasing Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a job as Misa-Misa's manager, besides, if I return to the police, I'd feel like a loser--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch what you say, Matsuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it possible to return to the police, and help out in my spare time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.59,0:14:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. {\alpha&HFF&}If you're planning to return to the police, please don't come here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. If you're planning to return to the police, please don't come here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I won't reveal a single thing from this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.59,0:14:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely won't give you any information from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.59,0:14:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to pursue Kira as a lone policeman, then that's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it'd be right for you to quit as a police officer, and then go chasing Kira to the point of causing your family concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly as Ryuuzaki says. {\alpha&HFF&}If you decide to stop now, no one will blame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly as Ryuuzaki says. If you decide to stop now, no one will blame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. {\alpha&HFF&}We won't think of you as a traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. We won't think of you as a traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Chief, you also have a family...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our circumstances are completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.65,0:15:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so unfair. {\alpha&HFF&}I wanted to stay as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so unfair. I wanted to stay as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.15,0:15:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I approached this knowing that my life was going to be at risk...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I quit now, how can I face Ukita?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! {\alpha&HFF&}Why has it become wrong for a police officer to chase Kira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Why has it become wrong for a police officer to chase Kira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki... {\alpha&HFF&}didn't you make me promise that if anything happens to any member of the investigation, including being fired by the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.69,0:15:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki... didn't you make me promise that if anything happens to any member of the investigation, {\alpha&HFF&}including being fired by the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki... didn't you make me promise that if anything happens to any member of the investigation, including being fired by the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would provide them and their family with sufficient financial aid for a lifetime?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you reluctant to tell them this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your own business, Watari.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.56,0:15:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? {\alpha&HFF&}You've even acted to protect our livelihood?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You've even acted to protect our livelihood?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.22,0:16:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that great, Aizawa-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, {\alpha&HFF&}were you testing me to see whether I'd leave the police and continue here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, were you testing me to see whether I'd leave the police and continue here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-{\alpha&HFF&}It isn't like that, Aizawa! Ryuuzaki just hates to say things like that himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It isn't like that, Aizawa! {\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuzaki just hates to say things like that himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.04,0:16:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It isn't like that, Aizawa! Ryuuzaki just hates to say things like that himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-{\alpha&HFF&}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.73,0:16:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.03,0:16:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.91,0:16:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was testing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.73,0:16:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see what choice he'd make.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.33,0:16:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I get it! {\alpha&HFF&}I'm leaving this investigation and returning to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.88,0:16:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I get it! I'm leaving this investigation and returning to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was unable to make an instant decision like you, {\alpha&HFF&}and was leaning towards returning to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.76,0:16:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was unable to make an instant decision like you, and was leaning towards returning to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to be stubborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF&}collisionline
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.37,0:16:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! {\alpha&HFF&}I quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.24,0:16:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just realized... {\alpha&HFF&}I hate Ryuuzaki, his methods, all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just realized... I hate Ryuuzaki, {\alpha&HFF&}his methods, all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just realized... I hate Ryuuzaki, his methods, all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:17:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Aizawa-san, {\alpha&HFF&}I like people that are like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Aizawa-san, I like people that are like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the other thing I hate! {\alpha&HFF&}The fact that you can say that with such a straight face!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.45,0:17:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the other thing I hate! The fact that you can say that with such a straight face!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.85,0:17:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for all your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've found another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A branch manager from one of Yotsuba's biggest rival banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,September 7th - slipped on the stairs at home and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,September 7th, that makes it a Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking a look at this again, {\alpha&HFF&}it just occurred to me that all the deaths which benefit Yotsuba happen towards the end of the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.32,0:17:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking a look at this again, it just occurred to me that all the deaths which benefit Yotsuba happen towards the end of the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.18,0:17:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? {\alpha&HFF&}Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.74,0:17:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first the times of death were random; {\alpha&HFF&}however, they've gradually begun to cluster around the time from Friday evening until Saturday afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.04,0:17:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first the times of death were random; however, they've gradually begun to cluster around the time from Friday evening until Saturday afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:17:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an excellent observation, Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep telling you that I'm not "Chief" anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.23,0:18:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. {\alpha&HFF&}To me, you'll always be the Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. To me, you'll always be the Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an excellent lead, father!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not planning to lose to you and Ryuuzaki just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.50,0:18:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be a dead weight around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.43,0:18:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dead weight...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kira a part of Yotsuba? {\alpha&HFF&}Is Kira merely using Yotsuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.48,0:18:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kira a part of Yotsuba? Is Kira merely using Yotsuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.88,0:18:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no idea which it is, {\alpha&HFF&}but we can assume that Kira is behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no idea which it is, but we can assume that Kira is behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.09,0:18:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time that we investigate Yotsuba thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.74,0:18:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finished compiling a list of all Yotsuba's employees, both here and overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over 300,000 people! {\alpha&HFF&}How did he manage this so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.93,0:18:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over 300,000 people! How did he manage this so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing, Mogi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was always something amazing about Mogi-san, right from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-{\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuzaki, is there anything else I can do? Other than being a manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ryuuzaki, {\alpha&HFF&}is there anything else I can do? Other than being a manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ryuuzaki, is there anything else I can do? {\alpha&HFF&}Other than being a manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ryuuzaki, is there anything else I can do? Other than being a manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.78,0:18:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to make yourself useful?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.01,0:18:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, can you bring me another cup of coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't forget our guests as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.68,0:19:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did they get in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.55,0:19:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're our new members.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Aiber, {\alpha&HFF&}a con artist. Nice to meet ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Aiber, a con artist. {\alpha&HFF&}Nice to meet ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.94,0:19:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Aiber, a con artist. Nice to meet ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Wedy, {\alpha&HFF&}a thief by trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Wedy, a thief by trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.48,0:19:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-{\alpha&HFF&}A con artist and a thief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A con artist and a thief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.90,0:19:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aiber acquires and learns what is necessary for every social discourse, and is guaranteed to form an intimate connection with his target.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.82,0:19:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be using him as our spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wedy is a thief that can crack any safe, key or security system.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As proof, she was able to infiltrate this place without anyone noticing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}We'll be investigating with criminals?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We'll be investigating with criminals?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.65,0:19:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're criminals, {\alpha&HFF&}but not the type that appear in public. Kira will not be able to judge them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.19,0:19:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're criminals, but not the type that appear in public. Kira will not be able to judge them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to think of them as professionals from the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. {\alpha&HFF&}In order to investigate Yotsuba properly, we'll need such people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.81,0:20:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. In order to investigate Yotsuba properly, we'll need such people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all work together on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.67,0:20:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi... {\alpha&HFF&}Eriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.23,0:20:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi... Eriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.59,0:20:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing in such a place?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to come home, just say so. {\alpha&HFF&}I haven't bought you any dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.02,0:20:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to come home, just say so. I haven't bought you any dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you half of my croquettes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.64,0:20:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... {\alpha&HFF&}I haven't had a lot of rest, so they've given me some leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.03,0:20:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I haven't had a lot of rest, so they've given me some leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Leave"? You have time off?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.78,0:20:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I should get some time off every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.36,0:20:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means we can come to this park... {\alpha&HFF&}even the zoo... or theme parks...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:21:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means we can come to this park... even the zoo... {\alpha&HFF&}or theme parks...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.77,0:21:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means we can come to this park... even the zoo... or theme parks...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.11,0:21:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama... {\alpha&HFF&}papa is crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.46,0:21:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama... papa is crying.
